arStrings.szText: When you cast an {c_important}Incarnate{/c} Skill enemies around you become {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. Killing a {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} enemy echoes {c_random}[Affix_Value_1*100|%|]{/c} of the killing blow's damage to another Nearby enemy.
